high_descs: move to the right to face the sink on the right
pick up the pink bar of soap out of the sink on the right
move to the left in between both sinks
pull out the drawer that is closest to the sink on the right and put the pink bar of soap in to the drawer and close the drawer
move to the left to face the sink on the left side
pick up the bar of soap that is sitting to the left of the sink on the left side
move to the right to face the drawer closest to the sink on the right
open the drawer and put the pink bar of soap in to the drawer on top of the other bar of soap
anns.task_desc: put two bars of soap in to the drawer

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the towel hanging on the bar then turn left and walk to the sink.
Pick up the soap that's in the sink.
Take a step backwards and then take a step to your left.
Open the drawer that's to the right of the middle of the sinks and put the soap in it's back left corner before closing it again.
Take several steps to your left so you are standing in front of the left sink.
Pick up the soap that's in front of you to the left of the left sink..
Walk back to where you put the first bar of soap.
Open the drawer where you put the first bar of soap and place this bar of soap on top of the first then close the drawer again.
anns.task_desc: Put two bars of soap in the drawer.
